The spiral is the usual “Ulam” spiral  

\[
\begin{array}{ccc}
5&4&3\\
6&1&2\\
7&8&9
\end{array}
\]

with 1 at \((0,0)\), the right direction as \(+x\) and the upward direction as \(+y\).

--------------------------------------------------------------------
### 1.  Coordinates of a given number  

For any integer \(n\) let  

\[
m=\text{the smallest odd integer }\ge \sqrt{n},\qquad  
k=\frac{m-1}{2}.
\]

The square of side \(m\) ends at the point \((k,-k)\) with value \(m^{2}\).  
If \(t=m^{2}-n\),

* \(0\le t<2k\)  (bottom side)  \((x,y)=(k-t,-k)\)
* \(2k\le t<4k\)  (left side)  \((x,y)=(-k,\,-k+(t-2k))\)
* \(4k\le t<6k\)  (top side)  \((x,y)=(-k+(t-4k),\,k)\)
* \(6k\le t<8k\)  (right side) \((x,y)=(k,\,k-(t-6k))\)

--------------------------------------------------------------------
### 2.  Position of 2026  

\[
\sqrt{2026}\approx45.0,\qquad m=47,\qquad k=23,\qquad m^{2}=2209.
\]

\(t = 2209-2026 = 183\).  
Since \(6k=138<183<8k=184\) we are on the **right side**:

\[
x=k=23,\qquad y=k-(t-6k)=23-(183-138)= -22 .
\]

Hence  

\[
2026\; \text{is at}\; (23,-22).
\]

--------------------------------------------------------------------
### 3.  The eight neighbours  

The eight surrounding coordinates are  

\[
\begin{aligned}
&(22,-23),\;(23,-23),\;(24,-23),\\
&(22,-22),\;(24,-22),\\
&(22,-21),\;(23,-21),\;(24,-21).
\end{aligned}
\]

For a point \((x,y)\) we first set \(k'=\max(|x|,|y|)\) and \(M=(2k'+1)^{2}\)
(the maximal value on that layer).  
According to the side on which \((x,y)\) lies we obtain its value
\(n=M-\text{offset}\) using the same formulas as above.

Carrying this out:

| coordinate | value |
|------------|-------|
| (22,‑23)   | 2208 |
| (23,‑23)   | 2209 |
| (24,‑23)   | 2210 |
| (22,‑22)   | 2025 |
| (24,‑22)   | 2211 |
| (22,‑21)   | 1850 |
| (23,‑21)   | 2027 |
| (24,‑21)   | 2212 |

--------------------------------------------------------------------
### 4.  Sum of the neighbours  

\[
\begin{aligned}
\text{Sum} &= 2208+2209+2210+2025+2211+1850+2027+2212\\
           &= 16\,952 .
\end{aligned}
\]

--------------------------------------------------------------------
\[
\boxed{16\,952}
\]
